## {% textSize textSize="h3" inline=true _language="" %}How Idaho Access sends abortion pills{% /textSize %}

- Idaho Access accepts email requests for abortion pills from people in&nbsp;Idaho, Arizona, Nebraska, North & South Dakota, and Oklahoma
- **Email: {% inlineLink action={discriminant: ""} _language="" %}idahoaccess@proton.me{% /inlineLink %}**
- Idaho Access requests that people ask for abortion pills in their message, and include a name, mailing address and the date of the first day of last menstrual period.
- Detailed instructions are on this website:&nbsp;{% inlineLink action={discriminant: "external", value: {url: "https://www.redstateaccess.org/how-to-use-abortion-pills", showPopup: false}} _language="" %}https://www.redstateaccess.org/how-to-use-abortion-pills{% /inlineLink %}
- For secure communications, they recommend using {% inlineLink action={discriminant: ""} _language="" %}Proton Mail{% /inlineLink %}. Open a free account {% inlineLink action={discriminant: ""} _language="" %}here{% /inlineLink %}.
